	"system": {
		"description": "<p><em>Passive: You gain resistance to fire damage.</em></p><p><em><strong>Legend Dice Feature</strong></em><strong> — Burning Reversal:</strong> When a creature within 5 feet hits you with a melee weapon attack, you can expend a Legend Die as a reaction. The attacker takes fire damage equal to the result, and must succeed on a Dexterity saving throw (Maneuver DC) or catch fire, taking 1d6 fire damage at the start of its turns for 1 minute or until they use an action to put out the fire.</p>",
